## Release Types

| Type | Description | Approval Required |
|------|-------------|-------------------|
| Major | New baseline release | CCB + Gate Review |
| Minor | Incremental update | CCB |
| Patch | Corrections only | Configuration Manager |

## Release Naming

Releases follow the pattern: `{{ model_code }}-REL-{MAJOR}.{MINOR}.{PATCH}`

## Release Process

1. **Prepare** — Verify all items are baselined
2. **Review** — Gate review (for major releases)
3. **Approve** — CCB approval
4. **Package** — Create release package
5. **Distribute** — Publish to authorized recipients
6. **Archive** — Store release record

## Release Checklist

- [ ] All ECOs implemented and verified
- [ ] Baseline established and approved
- [ ] Traceability matrix updated
- [ ] Quality review completed
- [ ] Release notes prepared
